By the way, of the war scenes in Iraq and Afghanistan, numerous videos have already been loaded onto the platform in use, but this "gatting" has only recently been discovered by the British.
The Americans, however, advertise something different, namely with the free downloadable shooting game "America Army", in which the player can slip into the soldier's skin in the context of a more or less life-like simulation.
